snippet.title: Meri Bassai | मेरी बास्सै | Ep - 784 | Dec 06, 2022 | Nepali Comedy | Surbir, Ramchandra | Media Hub
snippet.description:
Meri Bassai is one of the longest and most popular Nepali comedy serials with 17 Years of broadcasting. Based on rural lifestyle and lower-middle-class people, the series represents many political and social issues on its episodes with educational comedy flavor. It is aired in Nepal Television at 8:50 PM and in YouTube at 9:30 PM every Tuesday. This show is produced by Media Hub Pvt. Ltd. 

The story is based on the rural lifestyle and lower-middle-class people. The show represents many political as well as social issues on its episodes with educational comedy flavour.

Production: Media Hub Pvt. Ltd.
Production Advisor: Som Dhital
Direction: Diwakar Bhandari
Editor: Rabin Bhatta
Sub-Editor: Ashok Chaudhary/Sarita Gautam
IT Manager/Publicity Design : Dibash Humagain
Script Writer: Kunjan Bhattarai/Diwakar Bhandari
Camera: Rahul Rai
Makeup: Pabitra Bhattarai
Title song Writer: Shankar Adhikari 
Music/Singer: Chetan Sapkota

Artists: Laxmi Giri, Keshav Prasad Pandit(Surbir), Ramchandra Adhikari, Surendra K.C, Palpasa Dangol, Niru Khadka, Tika bhakta Jirel,  Lekhant Bhusal, Diwakar Bhandari, Binam Kandel, Madhu Acharya, Ramesh Magar, Sarswoti Fuyal, Dhirendra Chand and many more.
Guest Artist : Mukunda Shrestha

snippet.title: इन्जिनियर सागर ढकालको यक्ष प्रश्न- काङ्ग्रेसमा राणा शासन,जनता काकाकुल ?
snippet.description:
- इन्जिनियर सागर ढकालको यक्ष प्रश्न- काङ्ग्रेसमा राणा शासन,जनता काकाकुल ?

यक्ष प्रश्न हिमालय टेलिभिजनबाट हरेक आइतबार र बुधबार राति ९ बजे प्रसारण हुने र समसामयिक विषयका बारेमा उक्त विषयमा विशेष दख्खल राख्ने व्यक्तित्वसँग गरिने टेलिभिजन अन्तर्वार्ता हो। कार्यक्रम प्रस्तोता राजेन्द्र बानियाँ लोकप्रिय टिभी जर्नालिस्ट हुनुहुन्छ।

कार्यक्रम यक्ष प्रश्नको २१०  औं एपिसोडमा  सागर ढकालसंगको यो विशेष कुराकानी ।

Yaksha Prashna with #RajendraBaniya in conversation with Sagar Dhakal 
Presenter: Rajendra Baniya
Guest: Sagar Dhakal 
#RajendraBaniya #sagardhakal #YakshaPrashna  #election2022  
About us
.
Himalaya Television, named after the mighty Himalayas, is a channel that has a vision beyond the conventional vogues of broadcasting. Our ambition is not solely to show but also to raise awareness of human issues and embrace the heterogeneous needs of a multicultural society. Himalaya Television reaches out to all the people of Nepal from the plains of the Terai to the high lands of the Himalayas and to those struggling for their livelihood abroad. Himalaya Television Network (HTV), one of the top premium infotainment Satellite Television channels in the Nation started in the year 2010 and has been successfully able to create its identity in a short span of time.

localized.description:
- इन्जिनियर सागर ढकालको यक्ष प्रश्न- काङ्ग्रेसमा राणा शासन,जनता काकाकुल ?

यक्ष प्रश्न हिमालय टेलिभिजनबाट हरेक आइतबार र बुधबार राति ९ बजे प्रसारण हुने र समसामयिक विषयका बारेमा उक्त विषयमा विशेष दख्खल राख्ने व्यक्तित्वसँग गरिने टेलिभिजन अन्तर्वार्ता हो। कार्यक्रम प्रस्तोता राजेन्द्र बानियाँ लोकप्रिय टिभी जर्नालिस्ट हुनुहुन्छ।

कार्यक्रम यक्ष प्रश्नको २१०  औं एपिसोडमा  सागर ढकालसंगको यो विशेष कुराकानी ।

Guest: Sagar Dhakal 
#RajendraBaniya #sagardhakal #YakshaPrashna  #election2022

Magne Buda as सुकुम्बासी | Kedar Prasad Ghimire | Sukumbasi | Nepali Movie Scene

Movie: CHHA EKAN CHHA
Director: Dinesh D.C
Producer: Deepakraj Giri, Dipashree Nirula , Niramal Sharma
Story: Deepakraj Giri
Cast: Neeta Dhungana, Deepakraj Giri, Kiran KC, Jitu Nepal, Kedar Ghimire, Sandip Chhetri, Shivahari Paudel

Nepali movie ‘Chha Ekan Chha’ is a comedy film by the well known comedy actors of television. The lead actors in the movie are the well known comedy actors of ‘Tito Satya’, ‘Meri Bassai’ and ‘Jire Khursani’. The movie is produced by the makers of ‘Tito Satya’ – Deepak Raj Giri, Deepa Shree Niraula and Nirmal Sharma (Gaida). The film is directed by Dinesh DC. The lead actress of the movie, Neeta Dhungana, is considered an actress with a lot of potential in the Nepali film industry.

snippet.title: The Kapil Sharma Show Season 2 | Kajol Meets "Ajay Devgn" | Ep 284 | FE | 3 Dec 2022
snippet.description:
Synopsis: Kajol Meets "Ajay Devgn" 
 --------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
The host, Kapil Sharma, makes a rocking entry to the stage and talks about how parents are with their children. He compliments Archana Puran Singh and they share a hilarious banter. He shares some funny talks and how now times are different from the past and how children are also smart now. Then the evergreen, Kajol makes an entry, and Kapil introduces her, and she talks about her film Salaam Venky and what it depicts. This starts a hilarious night of fun, watch the full episode to know more.

Show Name: The Kapil Sharma Show Season 2 
Guests - Kajol, Vishal Jethwa, and Revathi.
Episode: 284 - 3 Dec 2022
Producers: Kapil Sharma, Salman Khan, Deepak Dhar

#thekapilsharmashow #uditnarayan #adityanarayan #deepanarayanjha #shwetaagarwal #setindia #दीकपिलशर्माशो

----------------------------------------------------------------
Kapil Sharma is back with his gang - Bindu, Chandan, and 'mohalle ki dhoban' Gudiya. In tow is a new character, Maski, along with Goli, Roopmati, and more! Enjoy guaranteed laughter with Kapil and his antics as different celebrities join in.
